reviewText: I love it so much that I drive my family crazy by watching it all the time

Like any other Good Eats episodes. These follow the formula that has made Alton Brown a hero to legions of new and novice cooks as well as the science nerds that can rock a souffl in the kitchen.

I just wish he would do another season or 5.

Are you tired and bored of Food Channel telling you where to Eat? Does your food bills become a lot smaller than your take out bills? Remember when when that kitchen smelled great when it's Sunday 4:00/pm? I do.  through step by step directions and with a splash of comedy you to can cook something that will smell and taste great. These were the best of FOOD Channel. HEY FOOD NETWORK I AM TIRED OF DRIVE-INS AND DIVES Lets stay home and cook up something in the kitchen. Can't go wrong with Brown.
